  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Radio Waves, support to community radio stations in Zambia - SCALE UP</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will support an additional four stations as part of the Radio Waves project which gives people a platform on which they can voice their concerns and demand answers from those in power. The new stations will receive a range of training and in addition,we are working with the Media Institute of Southern Africa (MISA) to monitor how media platforms across Zambia cover key governance issues and political campaigning around the national Presidential elections in 2016.</narrative>
